---
/**
 * Inline Lucide icons. No runtime, no emoji.
 * Add to the `icons` map as needed. Stroke is currentColor so it inherits text color.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   <Icon name="phone" class="h-5 w-5 text-brand-red" />
 */

